      <title>会议纪要显示，如果物价不下跌，台湾可能再次加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/taiwan-may-hike-rates-again-if-prices-don-t-fall-minutes-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周四发布的会议纪要，台湾货币管理局董事会的一名成员警告说，如果未来几个月通胀没有缓解，台湾央行可能不得不进一步加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/taiwan-may-hike-rates-again-if-prices-don-t-fall-minutes-show</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:54:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员称游说重新考虑卢比衍生品规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/traders-said-to-lobby-for-rethinking-of-rupee-derivatives-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度交易员正计划推动重新考虑一项要求货币衍生品具有基础风险敞口的规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/traders-said-to-lobby-for-rethinking-of-rupee-derivatives-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:54:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德意志银行在新的成本逆风中将邮政银行工资提高 12.5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/deutsche-bank-raises-postbank-pay-by-12-5-in-new-cost-headwind</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行已同意将其大量德国员工的工资提高 12.5%，这增加了首席执行官 Christian Sewing 的成本压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/deutsche-bank-raises-postbank-pay-by-12-5-in-new-cost-headwind</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:24:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于买家在陷入困境的市场中观望，可可再次暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/cocoa-slumps-again-as-buyers-hold-back-in-troubled-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于流动性枯竭和商业买家不愿购买可可豆，可可价格再次下跌，延续了一周的剧烈波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/cocoa-slumps-again-as-buyers-hold-back-in-troubled-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:14:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本可能在最近的日元干预中花费约 230 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/boj-accounts-signal-japan-s-second-yen-intervention-in-fed-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据彭博社对央行账户的分析，日本本周可能进行第二次货币干预，这是其为支撑日元而加剧的另一个迹象。]]></description>
