      <title>垃圾发行人为债券销售增加保障措施以吸引贷方</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/multiversity-adds-investor-protections-to-1-1-billion-bond-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[垃圾借款人 Multiversity SpA、Motel One GmbH 和 La Doria SpA 周四调整了计划债券销售的条款，以吸引因近期高收益市场动荡而感到不安的投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/multiversity-adds-investor-protections-to-1-1-billion-bond-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:46:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>创纪录的现金需求引发人们猜测英国央行将结束债券销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/record-repo-demand-spurs-speculation-boe-will-end-bond-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，周四英国央行的现金需求跃升至创纪录的 122 亿英镑（153 亿美元），这是一系列增加的最新举措，可能会刺激政策制定者在几个月内通过债券市场放松金融状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/record-repo-demand-spurs-speculation-boe-will-end-bond-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
